Yep so finally my new map surf_Sunset2 is finished!

It needed a long time to create this so I hope all of you enjoy playing and surfing it. 

Map details:
- 6 Stages
- 1 Bonus 
- 1 Secret
- Jailsystem
- 5 minutes to surf
- medium/hard-surf

Thanks go to:
- Sangre: for helping me with fixing a bug and for just being a great guy ^^
- Lightning: he hade the surf-video u can watch on youtube :D also first beta test was on his server. thx buddy! VIDEO--> http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ulmzrxI1noY&feature=recentlik (not available in germany -.-)
- Untouch: getting the second beta test server started xD thx buddy i couldn'thave done this without ur help! 
- Billy: great advices :D
- All beta testers: yeah for finding bugs and so on...

so I hope u like my new map and will have fun with it :)
